x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/bjork-skepta@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/apple">Apple Music</a>公布了跨年夜直播活动的阵容。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/big-reads/bjork-cover-interview-2022-fossora-3318517">比约克：“首先你创造一个有声音的宇宙，然后你进入它”</a></strong></li></ul><p>为了迎接 2025 年的到来，Apple Music 为其两场除夕夜直播聚集了不拘一格的表演阵容，均名为<em>Apple Music Live: NYE</em> 。第一场直播将由<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bjork">Björk</a>表演一组罕见的 DJ，Apple Music 的 Tim Sweeney 和伦敦 DJ Naina 也将进行表演。这些表演是在伦敦 The Cause 录制的，并将于 12 月 31 日晚上 9 点（格林威治标准时间）通过<a href="http://apple.co/_Club" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Apple Music Club</a>和<a href="http://apple.co/am-1" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Apple Music 1</a>进行直播。</p><p>上述比约克、斯威尼和奈娜的作品将以纯音频流的形式播出。</p><p>从格林威治标准时间晚上 11 点开始，第二轮<em>Apple Music Live：除夕</em>庆祝活动即将拉开帷幕，这次是以视频形式， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/skepta">Skepta</a>和 Uncle Waffles 的表演也录制在 The Cause 中。这些演出将在<a href="https://music.apple.com/us/curator/apple-music-dj-mixes/1441811365" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Apple Music</a> 、 <a href="http://apple.co/_Club" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Apple Music Club</a>和<a href="http://apple.co/am-1" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Apple Music 1</a>上播放。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/DDuN5qFpJw1/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; wid