替补队员斯利姆·邓拉普去世，享年 73 岁https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-replacements-slim-dunlap-has-died-ged-73-3823586?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=the-replacements-slim-dunlap-has-died- 73岁Surej SinghThu, 19 Dec 2024 04:55:42 +0000 Music NewsNews..Rock https://www.nme.com/?p=3823586 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/slim-dunlap-the-replacements@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/slim-dunlap-the-replacements@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/slim-dunlap-the-replacements@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/slim-dunlap-the-replacements@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/slim-dunlap-the-replacements@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/slim-dunlap-the-replacements@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/slim-dunlap-the-replacements@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这位吉他手于 1987 年加入乐队，并在他们最后两张专辑中演奏</p><p>The Replacements 成员斯利姆<a href="https://www.nme.com">·邓</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-replacements-slim-dunlap-has-died-aged-73-3823586">拉普 (Slim Dunlap) 去世，享年 73 岁</a></p>; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/slim-dunlap-the-replacements@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/slim-dunlap-the-replacements@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/slim-dunlap-the-replacements@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/slim-dunlap-the-replacements@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/slim-dunlap-the-replacements@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/slim-dunlap-the-replacements@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/slim-dunlap-the-replacements@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-replacements">The Replacements 乐队</a>的吉他手 Bob &#39;Slim&#39; Dunlap 去世，享年 73 岁。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/musician-deaths-2024-obituaries-3822913">记住我们在 2024 年失去的音乐传奇人物</a></strong></li></ul><p>据<a href="https://www.startribune.com/placeholder-obit-copy-for-slim-dunlap-do-not-publish-story-is-hidden-in-chorus/601196590" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《明尼苏达明星论坛报》</em></a>报道，邓拉普周三在明尼阿波利斯的家中去世。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-replacements-12-1256045">2012年，他患上了使人衰弱的中风</a>，此后健康状况一直不佳。他的家人向 MST 证实了他的死讯：“鲍勃今天中午 12 点 48 分在家中去世，家人在身边。我们给他播放了他的《Live at the Turf Club》（《谢谢你的舞者！）》CD，他在听完他版本的《Hillbilly Heaven》后不久就离开了我们——非常令人心酸。这是过去一周的自然下降。总的来说，这是由于中风并发症造成的。”</p><p> Slim Dunlap 于 20 世纪 70 年代初开始了他的音乐生涯，曾在明尼苏达州双城的多个乐队中演奏，其中包括 Curtis Almsted 的 Spooks。在 Spooks 任职期间，邓拉普引起了 The Replacements 成员 Paul Westerberg 的注意。当时，韦斯特伯格正在寻找一位吉他手来取代美国朋克乐队的领军人物鲍勃·斯廷顿（Bob Stinton），鲍勃·斯廷顿因未能妥善处理药物滥用问题而离开。 </p><figure id="attachment_3823593" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3823593" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3823593" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/the-replacements-slim-dunlap@2000x1270.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/the-replacements-slim-dunlap@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/the-replacements-slim-dunlap@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/the-replacements-slim-dunlap@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/the-replacements-slim-dunlap@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/the-replacements-slim-dunlap@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/the-replacements-slim-dunlap@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3823593" class="wp-caption-text">鲍勃·“斯利姆”·邓拉普。图片来源：Jim Steinfeldt/Michael Ochs Archives/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p> Dunlap 于 1987 年加入 The Replacements，当时他们录制了专辑“Pleased To Meet Me”。他一直留在乐队直到 1991 年乐队解散，并出现在他们的最后两张专辑中。 1989 年的《Don&#39;t Tell A Soul》和 1990 年的《All Shook Down》。</p><p>在 The Replacements 解散后，Slim Dunlap 于 1993 年发行了他的首张个人专辑《The Old New Me》，并于 1996 年发行了后续专辑《Times Like This》。2002 年，他录制了现场专辑《Live at the Turf Club》（感谢You Dancers!)”在圣保罗可容纳 350 人的赛马俱乐部举行——该专辑于 2020 年发行。</p><p>邓拉普一直活跃在明尼苏达音乐界，直到 2012 年遭遇严重中风，导致他大部分瘫痪。疾病消息传出后，The Replacements 的保罗·韦斯特伯格 (Paul Westerberg) 和汤米·斯廷森 (Tommy Stinson)<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-replacements-12-1256045">再次联合组成 EP，为邓拉普的医疗费用筹集资金</a>。</p><p> 2014年，The Replacements被提名入选摇滚名人堂，但最终未能获得这一荣誉。</p><p>自从中风以来，邓拉普一直卧床不起， <a href="https://www.cbsnews.com/minnesota/news/slim-dunlap-estate-sale-minneapolis-the-replacements/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">去年歌迷们开始从他的家人那里购买这位音乐家的纪念品，</a>以帮助支付他的医疗费用。</p><p> The Replacements 成员斯利姆<a href="https://www.nme.com">·邓</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-replacements-slim-dunlap-has-died-aged-73-3823586">拉普 (Slim Dunlap) 去世，享年 73 岁</a></p>;
史努比狗狗不喜欢德雷克因《不像我们》而对环球音乐集团提起法律诉讼：“我们在街上开庭” https://www.nme.com/news/music/snoop-dogg-isnt-a-fan-of-drakes-legal-action-against-umg-for-not-like-us-we-hold-court-在街上-3823566？u tm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=snoop-dogg-isnt-a-fan-of-drakes-legal-action-against-umg-for-not-like-us-we-hold-court-in-the-streetsSurej Singh Thu, 19 Dec 2024 04:03:24 +0000 Music NewsNewsRap https://www.nme.com/?p=3823566 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/snoop-dogg-drake@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/snoop-dogg-drake@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/snoop-dogg-drake@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/snoop-dogg-drake@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/snoop-dogg-drake@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/snoop-dogg-drake@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/snoop-dogg-drake@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这位说唱偶像还因在社交媒体上分享 Drake 的“Taylor Made Freestyle”而向 Kendrick Lamar 道歉</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/snoop-dogg-isnt-a-fan-of-drakes-legal-action-against-umg-for-not-like-us-we-hold-court-in-the-streets-3823566">史努比狗狗 (Snoop Dogg) 不喜欢德雷克 (Drake) 因《不像我们》而对环球音乐集团 (UMG) 提起的法律诉讼：“我们在街头开庭”</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/snoop-dogg-drake@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/snoop-dogg-drake@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/snoop-dogg-drake@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/snoop-dogg-drake@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/snoop-dogg-drake@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/snoop-dogg-drake@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/snoop-dogg-drake@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/snoop-dogg">Snoop Dogg</a>分享了他对<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/drake">Drake</a>就<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kendrick-lamar">Kendrick Lamar</a>的《Not Like Us》向<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/universal-music-group">环球音乐集团</a>提起法律诉讼的看法 - 了解更多信息。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/snoop-dogg-missionary-review-3821875">《史努比狗狗》——《传教士》评论：嘻哈经典的平庸续集</a></strong></li></ul><p>德雷克最近对环球音乐集团提起了两起与“不像我们”有关的法律纠纷，这起纠纷源于<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/drake-and-kendrick-lamars-feud-the-full-timeline-3754820">今年早些时候他们的激烈争执</a>。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/drake-kendrick-lamar-not-like-us-universal-spotify-artificially-inflated-allegation-3815805">第一起纠纷在纽约提起，指控环球音乐集团“人为夸大”《不像我们》的流媒体播放量</a>，并涉及未公开的“付费播放”计划。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/drake-umg-second-legal-action-not-like-us-kendrick-lamar-3816253">第二起争议是在德克萨斯州提起的，指控诽谤</a>，声称UMG“故意”批准发行《Not Like Us》，尽管肯德里克·拉马尔的歌词声称德雷克是“恋童癖”。 </p><figure id="attachment_3780765" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3780765" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3780765" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/drake-performs-live-2022.jpg" alt="德雷克" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/drake-performs-live-2022.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/drake-performs-live-2022-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/drake-performs-live-2022-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/drake-performs-live-2022-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/drake-performs-live-2022-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/drake-performs-live-2022-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3780765" class="wp-caption-text"> 2022 年 12 月 9 日，德雷克 (Drake) 在州立农场竞技场 (State Farm Arena)。图片来源：Prince Williams/Wireimage</figcaption></figure><p>肯德里克·拉马尔 (Kendrick Lamar) 的团队尚未回应<em>《NME</em> 》的置评请求。与此同时，环球音乐集团就这两份文件表示：“有关环球音乐集团会采取任何措施损害其任何艺人的说法是无礼且不真实的。我们在营销和促销活动中采用最高的道德实践。在这份诉讼前提交的材料中，再多的人为和荒谬的法律论据也无法掩盖粉丝选择他们想听的音乐的事实。”</p><p>现在，史努比狗狗——尽管过去曾支持肯德里克，但<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/snoop-dogg-responds-to-kendrick-lamar-lyric-about-him-supporting-drake-on-new-album-3815281">在社交媒体上分享了德雷克的“Taylor Made Freestyle”片段后，陷入了两位说唱歌手之间的争斗</a>——对这些法律文件有了一些想法。</p><p>史努比出现在<em>The Bootleg Kev 播客</em>最近一集宣传他的新专辑《<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/snoop-dogg-missionary-review-3821875">传教士</a>》的节目中，被问到他对德雷克的文件有何看法。在最初拒绝回答后，这位说唱歌手简短地回答道：“在西方，我们在街上开庭。我们就是这么称呼它的。” </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="史努比狗狗谈《传教士》、肯德里克 vs 德雷克、白宫吸烟、西海岸和 Eazy-E" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/JfnxtT1bNAY?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>然后他谈到了自己参与的不和，澄清自己站在肯德里克·拉马尔一边：“[拉马尔]是一名说唱歌手，他应该说出自己的想法并说出自己的真相。我是他的大宅男，所以我必须从他的角度来看他说的话，因为他说的是实话。当真相直接摆在我面前时，我愿意接受。”</p><p>史努比随后解释说，他不知道自己在社交媒体上发布了“Taylor Made Freestyle”：“我与某人合作发布了一个帖子。当我做[合作帖子]时，我不听音乐，我只看到“杜松子酒和果汁”，因为这是我的品牌。所以，当我发布它时，我想我发布了“Gin and Juice”，我不知道它是什么歌，我不喜欢每个人的音乐。然后我听到一句话：‘侄子不喜欢你所做的事。’</p><p>史努比狗狗随后表示，他删除了该帖子，并给肯德里克留下了一条简短的语音邮件：“侄子，我是史努比叔叔，我收到了你的消息，我表示歉意。我完蛋了。我的错。”</p><p> Snoop Dogg 的《传教士》获得了<em>NME</em>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/snoop-dogg-missionary-review-3821875">三星级评价</a>，Kyann-Sian Williams 写道：“《传教士》是一部平淡无奇的续集，鼓舞人心的基调让人感觉很牵强，声音的多功能性阻碍了整个项目。 Dre 和 Snoop 忘记了他们通过《Doggystyle》为西海岸创造的遗产，尽管其中不乏乐趣，但这个令人遗忘的系列仅仅触及了他们传奇地位的表面。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/snoop-dogg-isnt-a-fan-of-drakes-legal-action-against-umg-for-not-like-us-we-hold-court-in-the-streets-3823566">史努比狗狗 (Snoop Dogg) 不喜欢德雷克 (Drake) 因《不像我们》而对环球音乐集团 (UMG) 提起的法律诉讼：“我们在街头开庭”</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
戴夫·格罗尔 (Dave Grohl) 的女儿维奥莱特 (Violet) 正在准备她的首张专辑https://www.nme.com/news/music/dave-grohls-daughter-violet-is-preparing-her-debut-album-3823561?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=dave-grohls-daughter-violet-is-准备她的首张专辑Surej SinghThu, 19 Dec 2024 03:06:22 +0000 Music NewsNewsRockhttps://www.nme.com/?p=3823561 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dave-grohl-violet-grohl@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dave-grohl-violet-grohl@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dave-grohl-violet-grohl@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dave-grohl-violet-grohl@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dave-grohl-violet-grohl@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dave-grohl-violet-grohl@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dave-grohl-violet-grohl@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>她过去曾作为和声与喷火战机一起巡演</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/dave-grohls-daughter-violet-is-preparing-her-debut-album-3823561">Dave Grohl 的女儿 Violet 正在准备她的首张专辑的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dave-grohl-violet-grohl@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dave-grohl-violet-grohl@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dave-grohl-violet-grohl@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dave-grohl-violet-grohl@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dave-grohl-violet-grohl@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dave-grohl-violet-grohl@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dave-grohl-violet-grohl@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>据报道，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/dave-grohl">戴夫·格罗尔</a>的女儿维奥莱特正在制作她的首张专辑。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/foo-fighters-live-in-manchester-setlist-photos-3765719">喷火战机生活在曼彻斯特：所向无敌，仍然不可撼动</a></strong></li></ul><p>据<a href="https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/music-news/violet-grohl-debut-album-1236089338/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《好莱坞报道》</em></a>报道，据一位匿名消息人士透露，18 岁的维奥莱特“难以置信地致力于”“作为一名艺术家成长”并创作音乐。据报道，她还充分利用了父亲送给她的生日礼物——在工作室的时间。</p><p> Violet 的专辑并不是凭空出现的。早在 2018 年，她就开始<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/dave-grohls-daughter-singing-backing-vocals-foo-fighters-tour-2355599">与 Foo Fighters 一起上路</a>，在几场演出中为她父亲提供和声。</p><p>值得注意的是，Violet 曾在 2022 年为已故鼓手泰勒·霍金斯 (Taylor Hawkins) 举办的<a href="https://www.nme.com/big-reads/taylor-hawkins-tribute-concert-wembley-foo-fighters-cover-3306358">致敬音乐会上</a>与他们一起表演<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/taylor-hawkins">，</a>在那里她翻唱了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jeff-buckley">杰夫·巴克利 (Jeff Buckley</a> ) 的《Last Goodbye》和《Grace》以及<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-zutons">Zutons</a>的《Valerie》。</p><p>从那时起，她与乐队一起演出了几次，甚至去年在格拉斯顿伯里与他们一起<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/foo-fighters-dave-grohl-brings-out-daughter-violet-to-perform-show-me-how-at-glastonbury-2023-3460174">表演了戴夫为他母亲写的歌曲“Show Me How”</a> 。 </p><figure id="attachment_3823564" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3823564" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="wp-image-3823564 size-full" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/violet-grohl@2000x1270.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/violet-grohl@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/violet-grohl@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/violet-grohl@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/violet-grohl@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/violet-grohl@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/violet-grohl@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3823564" class="wp-caption-text">维奥莱特·格罗尔.图片来源：Emma McIntyre/Getty Images for The Recording Academy</figcaption></figure><p>根据<em>THR</em>的消息来源，维奥莱特被描述为“一位真正的火炬歌手。她的歌声非常棒。她非常有才华。”据报道，她还与制作人 Justin Raisen 合作制作这张专辑，后者曾与 Kim Gordon、Charli XCX 和 Sky Ferreira 等人合作过。</p><p> 2021 年 1 月， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/dave-grohl-wants-to-be-his-daughter-violets-drummer-its-one-of-my-dreams-2865975">戴夫称赞维奥莱特是“一位非常有才华的音乐家”</a> ，她可以“拿起一种乐器并在一周内学会它”。他补充道：“成为她的鼓手是我一生的梦想之一。”大约在那个时候，戴夫说维奥莱特正在考虑制作一张鞋凝视专辑，他想在上面演奏。</p><p>目前尚不清楚 Violet 的首张专辑是否仍会采用盯鞋风格，或者她的品味自 2021 年以来是否发生了变化。 </p><figure id="attachment_3537892" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3537892" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3537892" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/dave-and-violet-grohl-harry-durrant-1.jpg" alt="戴夫和维奥莱特·格罗尔" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/dave-and-violet-grohl-harry-durrant-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/dave-and-violet-grohl-harry-durrant-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/dave-and-violet-grohl-harry-durrant-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/dave-and-violet-grohl-harry-durrant-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/dave-and-violet-grohl-harry-durrant-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/dave-and-violet-grohl-harry-durrant-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3537892" class="wp-caption-text">戴夫·格罗尔和维奥莱特·格罗尔。图片来源：哈里·杜兰/盖蒂</figcaption></figure><p>今年九月，Foos 主唱戴夫·格罗尔 (Dave Grohl) 透露， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/dave-grohl-shares-that-hes-become-a-father-outside-of-my-marriage-3792457">他“最近成为了一个非婚生女儿的父亲”</a> 。他补充道：“我爱我的妻子和孩子，我正在尽一切努力重新获得他们的信任并赢得他们的原谅。”</p><p>乐队随后<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/foo-fighters-pull-out-of-soundside-music-festival-with-jack-white-replacing-the-band-3797478">取消了原定在 Soundside 音乐节上的头条节目</a>。喷火战机目前在他们的日历中没有任何直播日期。</p><p>在格罗尔的新女儿被曝光后，这位音乐家的代表<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/dave-grohls-representatives-debunk-viral-love-child-post-circulating-on-social-media-3793929">揭穿了社交媒体上疯传的“私生子”帖子</a>，其中一名 Instagram 用户声称自己是孩子的母亲。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/dave-grohls-daughter-violet-is-preparing-her-debut-album-3823561">Dave Grohl 的女儿 Violet 正在准备她的首张专辑的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
利亚姆·加拉格尔 (Liam Gallagher) 将节日经典歌曲命名为他最喜欢的圣诞歌曲https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-gallagher-names-holiday-classic-as-his-favourite-christmas-song-3823558?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=liam-gallagher-names-holiday-他最喜欢的经典圣诞歌曲Surej SinghThu, 19 Dec 2024 02:17:58 +0000 Music NewsNewsBritpopPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3823558 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/liam-gallagher@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/liam-gallagher@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/liam-gallagher@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/liam-gallagher@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/liam-gallagher@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/liam-gallagher@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/liam-gallagher@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这不是约翰·列侬之前支持的《战争结束》</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-gallagher-names-holiday-classic-as-his-favourite-christmas-song-3823558">利亚姆·加拉格尔 (Liam Gallagher) 将假日经典命名为他最喜欢的圣诞歌曲，</a>该帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/liam-gallagher@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/liam-gallagher@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/liam-gallagher@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/liam-gallagher@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/liam-gallagher@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/liam-gallagher@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/liam-gallagher@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/liam-gallagher">利亚姆·加拉格尔 (Liam Gallagher)</a>命名了他最喜欢的圣诞歌曲 - 看看下面是什么。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/oasis-artists-fans-talk-reunion-3800899"><b>“他们教会了我用音乐打动人心意味着什么”：艺术家谈绿洲的影响力</b></a></strong></li></ul><p>昨晚（12月17日），加拉格尔在推特上回答了几个粉丝的问题。在一个问题中，一位粉丝向这位<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/oasis">绿洲</a>歌手询问他最喜欢的圣诞歌曲。加拉格尔简洁地回答：“‘去年圣诞节’<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/wham">威猛</a>”。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">去年圣诞节威猛</p><p>— 利亚姆·加拉格尔 (@liamgallagher) <a href="https://twitter.com/liamgallagher/status/1868924227996598643?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2024 年 12 月 17 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>几位粉丝回复同意加拉格尔的选择，但一位粉丝很快对加拉格尔没有选择<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/john-lennon">约翰·列侬</a>的《战争结束》<a href="https://x.com/anonymoss_0/status/1868925154979688451" target="_blank" rel="noopener">表示惊讶</a>。事实上，利亚姆是《战争结束》的忠实粉丝，有一次他在讨论有史以来最好的圣诞歌曲时差点和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/noel-gallagher">哥哥诺埃尔</a>打起来。</p><p>诺埃尔<a href="https://www.radiox.co.uk/artists/noel-gallaghers-high-flying-birds/on-christmas-row-with-liam-over-slade-john-lennon/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在 2022 年透露，兄弟俩在酒吧时恢复了体力</a>：“最后实际上变成了暴力，因为他说约翰·列侬的歌曲《战争结束了》是有史以来最好的圣诞歌曲，我当时想， “我是斯莱德，‘大家圣诞快乐’。”这场争论变得如此激烈，人们不得不进来[说]‘等等，你在做什么？你们要为了一首圣诞歌曲而吵架吗？”</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/track/liam-gallaghers-new-song-all-youre-dreaming-review-2825673">评论：利亚姆·加拉格尔的《你梦想的一切》是一首感人的节日民谣</a></strong></li></ul><p>今年圣诞节，兄弟俩的日子似乎会更加顺利，因为他们在今年早些时候<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-reunion-tour-uk-ireland-stadium-2025-liam-noel-gallagher-tickets-3787539">透露了备受期待的绿洲乐队重返舞台</a>，并宣布明年夏天将<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-reunion-tour-uk-ireland-stadium-2025-liam-noel-gallagher-tickets-3787539">在英国和爱尔兰举行一系列大型体育场演出</a>。随后宣布了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-add-extra-dates-to-north-american-2025-reunion-tour-due-to-phenomenal-demand-3799159">北美</a>、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-announce-2025-south-american-reunion-tour-dates-the-brothers-are-coming-buy-tickets-3809661">南美</a>、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-add-more-dates-to-australia-2025-reunion-tour-3801693">澳大利亚</a>、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-announce-south-korean-and-japan-dates-for-their-2025-reunion-tour-3814881">韩国和日本</a>的日期。</p><p>在得知他们将回归后， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-respond-to-glastonbury-2025-rumours-and-the-chances-of-other-festivals-3788269">Oasis 排除了在 2025 年格拉斯顿伯里音乐节上进行头条表演的可能性</a>，并表示明年夏天他们不会出现在任何其他音乐节上。<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/could-oasis-return-to-knebworth-in-2026-3792709">利亚姆和诺埃尔也驳斥了 2026 年重返纳贝沃斯的传言</a>。</p><p>乐队宣布， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/cage-the-elephant">Cage The Elephant</a>将担任他们北美站的开场支持，而<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-confirm-richard-ashcroft-as-special-guest-for-2025-uk-and-ireland-reunion-tour-3804758">前 Verve 主唱兼独唱理查德·阿什克罗夫特 (Richard Ashcroft)</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-announce-cast-as-final-support-act-for-2025-uk-and-ireland-reunion-tour-3806934">卡斯特 (Cast)</a>将与曼彻斯特偶像一起参加他们在英国和爱尔兰的演出。</p><p>在其他新闻中， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-gallagher-now-denies-a-new-oasis-album-is-in-the-works-it-was-a-laugh-3813665">利亚姆最近反悔了他关于乐队目前正在录制一张新专辑的说法</a>，告诉歌迷“这很有趣”。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-gallagher-names-holiday-classic-as-his-favourite-christmas-song-3823558">利亚姆·加拉格尔 (Liam Gallagher) 将假日经典命名为他最喜欢的圣诞歌曲，</a>该帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
如果被驱逐，谢菲尔德的 Leadmill 可能会搬到新地点https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-leadmill-in-sheffield-could-move-to-new-location-if-evicted-3823532?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=the-leadmill-in-谢菲尔德如果被驱逐可以搬到新地点Aneesa AhmedWed, 18 Dec 2024 22:09:45 +0000 Music NewsNewsLive Music NewsPopRock https://www.nme.com/?p=3823532 <p><img width="2000" height="1240" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/The-Leadmill.-Credit-Gary-Wolstenholme.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="铅磨机。图片来源：Gary Wolstenholme" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/The-Leadmill.-Credit-Gary-Wolstenholme.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/The-Leadmill.-Credit-Gary-Wolstenholme-400x248.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/The-Leadmill.-Credit-Gary-Wolstenholme-800x496.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/The-Leadmill.-Credit-Gary-Wolstenholme-696x432.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/The-Leadmill.-Credit-Gary-Wolstenholme-1392x863.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/The-Leadmill.-Credit-Gary-Wolstenholme-1068x662.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>自业主于 2022 年发出驱逐通知以来，该场馆的未来一直充满不确定性</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-leadmill-in-sheffield-could-move-to-new-location-if-evicted-3823532">谢菲尔德的 Leadmill 如果被驱逐可能会搬到新地点的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1240" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/The-Leadmill.-Credit-Gary-Wolstenholme.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="铅磨机。图片来源：Gary Wolstenholme" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/The-Leadmill.-Credit-Gary-Wolstenholme.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/The-Leadmill.-Credit-Gary-Wolstenholme-400x248.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/The-Leadmill.-Credit-Gary-Wolstenholme-800x496.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/The-Leadmill.-Credit-Gary-Wolstenholme-696x432.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/The-Leadmill.-Credit-Gary-Wolstenholme-1392x863.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/The-Leadmill.-Credit-Gary-Wolstenholme-1068x662.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>该公司董事表示，位于谢菲尔德的标志性场所 The Leadmill 如果被驱逐，可能会搬到新地点。</p><p>自 2022 年以来，该场地一直受到威胁，此前该建筑的业主<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/artists-voice-support-for-sheffields-the-leadmill-as-iconic-venue-announces-eviction-and-closure-3195218">发布了驱逐通知</a>，引发了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/artists-voice-support-for-sheffields-the-leadmill-as-iconic-venue-announces-eviction-and-closure-3195218">整个音乐行业和演出观众的强烈抗议</a>。 Leadmill 的法律团队目前正在对该决定提出异议，声称该决定违反了多项法律。</p><p>据<em><a href="https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/articles/cvgn3yy40n2o?xtor=AL-99999-%5Bpartner%5D-%5BBBC+England%5D-%5Bheadline%5D-%5Bnews%5D-%5Bbizdev%5D-%5Bisapi%5D&amp;at_link_origin=BBCLookNorth&amp;at_medium=social&amp;at_link_id=778175C8-BD47-11EF-9235-F17F3A54A60E&amp;at_link_type=web_link&amp;at_ptr_name=twitter&amp;at_bbc_team=editorial&amp;at_campaign_type=owned&amp;at_format=link&amp;at_campaign=Social_Flow" target="_blank" rel="noopener">英国广播公司</a>报道，</em>该公司唯一董事菲尔米尔斯今天（12月18日）在利兹商业和财产法院举行的驱逐听证会上表示，在该市开设新场地可能是“可能的”。</p><p>米尔斯表示，搬到新地点的可能性是“假设的”和“B 计划或 C 计划”。导演表示，A 计划是“我们在这个案子中取得成功，并继续下去。”</p><p>这座可容纳 900 人的场馆大楼的所有者 Electric Group 于 2022 年 3 月向其租户 The Leadmill Ltd 发出了驱逐通知。Leadmill Ltd 拥有该场馆名称的商标，这意味着位于不同建筑的新场馆可以保留该名称以及原创的品牌。</p><p>然而，米尔斯表示，The Leadmill 的新址可能“不一定”位于谢菲尔德。 “如果我们在谢菲尔德找到合适的场所，我们实际上就是在与自己竞争，因为 The Leadmill 的名字和遗产在我们的客户心目中是不可分割的，”他说。</p><p> “[电气集团老板][多米尼克]马登先生在声明中表示，[场地]将永远被称为 The Leadmill，他说得很对。老特拉福德球场将永远被称为老特拉福德球场。”</p><p>本周早些时候，电气集团老板多米尼克·马登 (Dominic Madden)<a href="https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/articles/cy53w2q95gno" target="_blank" rel="noopener">指责</a>他的租户对场馆的翻新成本做出了“荒谬的过度”估计。</p><p>听证会继续进行。</p><p>当地新闻媒体<a href="https://www.thestar.co.uk/news/politics/plan-for-the-partial-demolition-of-sheffields-iconic-the-leadmill-building-submitted-4914758" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《谢菲尔德星报</em></a>》报道称，一项旨在部分拆除 The Leadmill 以改善“该地区的视觉特征”的新计划已<a href="https://www.thestar.co.uk/news/politics/plan-for-the-partial-demolition-of-sheffields-iconic-the-leadmill-building-submitted-4914758" target="_blank" rel="noopener">提交</a>，正在等待批准。谢菲尔德市议会的规划官员必须在 2 月 3 日之前就该提案的结果做出决定。</p><p>自 1980 年开业以来，这个独立场地曾接待过<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/coldplay">酷玩乐队 (Coldplay)</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-stone-roses">石玫瑰乐队 (The Stone Roses) 等乐队。</a></p><p> 2022 年，该场馆收到驱逐通知后，前<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/jeremy-corbyn-joins-campaign-to-save-sheffield-leadmill-3227527">工党领袖杰里米·科尔宾 (Jeremy Corbyn) 参观了 The Leadmill，并鼓励其他人“支持它……”</a> 。</p><p>他还呼应了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/leadmill-sheffield-eviction-closure-arctic-monkeys-tour-manager-local-reaction-3201505">无数谢菲尔德当地人的观点</a>，将其誉为“城市的心脏”，以及<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/local-stars-rally-around-leadmill-as-new-owners-register-for-name-electric-sheffield-3197594">谢菲尔德艺术家中的 Arctic Monkeys、Jarvis Cocker 和 Bring Me The Horizo​​n 的 Oli Sykes 等纷纷发声支持的场地</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-leadmill-in-sheffield-could-move-to-new-location-if-evicted-3823532">谢菲尔德的 Leadmill 如果被驱逐可能会搬到新地点的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
